    "The LITIV dataset [96] contains nine sequences, considering the effect of illumination in indoor captures.",
    "These datasets with limited sequences and low diversity have been depreciated.",
    "In 2016, for RGB-T tracking, Li et al.",
    "constructed the GTOT dataset which consists of 50 grayscale-thermal sequences.",
    "The data are mainly captured by a surveillance camera, covering different scenarios and conditions, such as dark night, rainy day, high illumination, etc."
